database.querier

Class Querier

  • java.lang.Object
    • database.querier.Querier
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FoodQuerier, UserQuerier

    public abstract class Querier
extends java.lang.Object
    Querier Abstract super-class of all queriers. Handles sql JDBC connections and provide I/O method interfaces.
